SCAN Associates Sdn Bhd Security Advisory

Products: Foxweb 2.5 (http://www.foxweb.com)
Date: 5th September 2003
Author: pokleyzz <pokleyzz_at_scan-associates.net>
Contributors:
    sk_at_scan-associates.net
